Method Detail

getActionKey

public abstract A getActionKey()
Get this mapped pair's action key

The action key is used to retrieve the MapperAction instance that is relevant to this pair (see the AbstractMapperActionFactory) where the MapperAction performs the map operation on this pair, queuing the result for output through the MapperAction's FlushAction.
